timeline.bodyText:
We would normally use a Precondition check here:
Preconditions.checkState(context.selectedColumns() == null, "Cannot ...");
I was also going to say that I think we should check the reverse as well, in case project is called before select, but it looks like the projection is tracked outside of the context for some reason. I don't think that's quite right. We probably want to move project to the context as well.
@edgarRd, do you know why project doesn't use the scan context?

